Taxamo,is,a,service,that,makes,it,easier,for,online,retailers,to,comply,with,EU,VAT,tax,laws,by,taking,care,of,EU,VAT,calculations,evidence,collection,EU,MOSS,settlement,and,audit,services,The,Taxamo,REST,API,enables,users,to,integrate,its,compliance,services,into,their,shopping,carts,or,e,commerce,software,Integrating,with,Taxamo,does,not,affect,the,customer,s,purchasing,experience